        "en": "An itinerary to discover the green giants of Etna and the volcanic remains of 1928. Starting from the Chiesetta di Magazzeni (Sant'Alfio/Milo) at ~1090 m, the route follows a well-marked forest track to the Fosse and Bocche di Santoro at ~1200 m. Gentle ascent, ideal for families and nature photographers."
